video_title: One SIMPLE habit to be more productive. #motivation
transcript:
one of the simplest habits that you can
have to being more productive is when
you don't feel like doing something get
your ass up off the couch out of the bed
turn the TV off put your phone away and
then just start moving whatever it is
you have to do you could do 50 jumping
jacks you could do 25 push-ups get your
body physically moving and that will
actually start to get you moving into
the direction that you want
